@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_elurmu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (v0 - tmp)
    v2 = (0.39 * ((v2 + 0.48 * tmp + 0.53) * tmp))
    v1 = (0.79 - (0.53 + v2))
    v1 = wp.abs((v1 * (v1 + 0.42 * v2 + 0.56)))
    v0 = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.74 / tmp + 0.59)) * (0.56 + 0.94))
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.abs((v2 + 0.78 * v0 + 0.01)))
    tmp = wp.sin((wp.cos(v2 + 0.70) + wp.abs(tmp + 0.17)))
    v0 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
